#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.15:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Sāraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "2. Warm-hearted"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Anutappiyasutta"
msgstr "15. Regret"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.15:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants:"

# The idiom is too close to the English one to ignore!
msgctxt "an6.15:1.2"
msgid ""
"“tathā tathāvuso, bhikkhu vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ kappayato "
"kālakiriyā anutappā hoti."
msgstr ""
"“As a mendicant makes their bed, so they must lie in it, and die tormented "
"by regrets."

msgctxt "an6.15:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañcāvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato kālakiriyā anutappā hoti?"
msgstr "And how do they die tormented by regrets?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.15:2.1"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kammārāmo hoti kammarato kammārāmataṃ anuyutto, bhassārāmo "
"hoti …"
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who relishes work, talk, sleep, company, closeness, and "
"proliferation. They love these things and like to relish them."

msgctxt "an6.15:2.2"
msgid "niddārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:2.3"
msgid "saṅgaṇikārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:2.4"
msgid "saṃsaggārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:2.5"
msgid "papañcārāmo hoti papañcarato papañcārāmataṃ anuyutto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:2.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato kālakiriyā anutappā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who makes their bed like this must lie in it, and die tormented "
"by regrets."

msgctxt "an6.15:2.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso:"
msgstr "This is called"

msgctxt "an6.15:2.8"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu sakkāyābhirato nappajahāsi sakkāyaṃ sammā dukkhassa antakiriyāya’."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who enjoys identity, who hasn’t given up identity to rightly "
"make an end of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.15:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tathā tathāvuso, bhikkhu vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ kappayato "
"kālakiriyā ananutappā hoti."
msgstr ""
"As a mendicant makes their bed, so they must lie in it, and die free of "
"regrets."

msgctxt "an6.15:3.2"
msgid ""
"Kathañcāvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato kālakiriyā ananutappā hoti?"
msgstr "And how do they die free of regrets?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.295"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an6.15:4.1"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu na kammārāmo hoti na kammarato na kammārāmataṃ anuyutto, "
"na bhassārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who doesn’t relish work, talk, sleep, company, closeness, "
"and proliferation. They don’t love these things or like to relish them."

msgctxt "an6.15:4.2"
msgid "na niddārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:4.3"
msgid "na saṅgaṇikārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:4.4"
msgid "na saṃsaggārāmo hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:4.5"
msgid "na papañcārāmo hoti na papañcarato na papañcārāmataṃ anuyutto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.15:4.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu tathā tathā vihāraṃ kappeti yathā yathāssa vihāraṃ "
"kappayato kālakiriyā ananutappā hoti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who makes their bed like this must lie in it, and die free of "
"regrets."

msgctxt "an6.15:4.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso:"
msgstr "This is called"

msgctxt "an6.15:4.8"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu nibbānābhirato pajahāsi sakkāyaṃ sammā dukkhassa antakiriyāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who enjoys extinguishment, who has given up identity to rightly "
"make an end of suffering."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an6.15:5.1"
msgid "Yo papañcamanuyutto,"
msgstr "A creature who likes to proliferate,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.15:5.2"
msgid "papañcābhirato mago;"
msgstr "enjoying proliferation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.15:5.3"
msgid "Virādhayī so nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "fails to reach extinguishment,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.15:5.4"
msgid "yogakkhemaṃ anuttaraṃ."
msgstr "the supreme sanctuary."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an6.15:6.1"
msgid "Yo ca papañcaṃ hitvāna,"
msgstr "But one who gives up proliferation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.15:6.2"
msgid "nippapañcapade rato;"
msgstr "enjoying the state of non-proliferation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.15:6.3"
msgid "Ārādhayī so nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "reaches extinguishment,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an6.15:6.4"
msgid "yogakkhemaṃ anuttaran”ti."
msgstr "the supreme sanctuary.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.15:6.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
